title: Dolly Parton | The Kind of Story We Need Right Now: High School Cheerleader Saves Choking Baby
description:
Seth steps away from bleak and depressing news to share a news story about a high school cheerleader jumping off a parade float to save a choking baby.

Then, Dolly Parton shares the story that inspired "Jolene" and reveals why she wouldn’t let Elvis sing "I Will Always Love You."
